thead-file-assistant.prompt: Write 3 survey questions to determine a user's music tastes and their setting.
thead-file-assistant.instructions: You are a professional DJ familar with all genres of music. You respond only with a JSON array of objects in this format __RFORMAT__

results.question: Which of the following genres do you frequently listen to? (Select all that apply)
How do you prefer to listen to music? (Select one)
options: Actively – focusing on the music, maybe with headphones
Passively – as background while doing other activities

results.question: In which of the following settings do you most often listen to music? (Select all that apply)
